                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.51/5011: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1927-02-07T15:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 7, 1927—3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>50. Your 114, February 5, 9 p.m. I do not desire you to participate in
                    representations of the kind described in paragraph 3 of your telegram.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
